#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Dutiyavagga → rajjavaggo (bj) | rajjavaggo dutiyo (pts2)
msgctxt "sn4.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. Rule "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Pāsāṇasutta "
msgstr "11. Boulders "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.244, sc1
msgctxt "sn4.11:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak Mountain. "

msgctxt "sn4.11:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā rattandhakāratimisāyaṃ abbhokāse nisinno hoti, devo ca ekamekaṃ phusāyati. "
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha was meditating in the open during the dark of night, while a gentle rain drizzled down. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.11:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā bhagavato bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato avidūre mahante pāsāṇe padālesi. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, wanting to make the Buddha feel fear, terror, and goosebumps, approached him, and crushed some large boulders close by him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn4.11:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā “māro ayaṃ pāpimā” iti viditvā māraṃ pāpimantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha, knowing that this was Māra the Wicked, addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.1"
msgid "“Sacepi kevalaṃ sabbaṃ, "
msgstr "“Even if you shake "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: calessasi → caleyyāsi (bj, mr) | gaḷeyyasi (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.2"
msgid "gijjhakūṭaṃ calessasi; "
msgstr "this entire Vulture’s Peak, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.3"
msgid "Neva sammāvimuttānaṃ, "
msgstr "the rightly released, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.11:3.4"
msgid "buddhānaṃ atthi iñjitan”ti. "
msgstr "the awakened, are unshaken.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.11:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
